If you are into Marketing, Business, or if you wish to find a job as a Web Application or Mobile Application Developer or a Software Engineer this track is the one for you.
During the first week of the JavaScript track, you will be introduced to JavaScript and will then move on to Advanced JavaScript. Later on, the track will cover React.JS. From week 9 of the track, you have to work on the previous courses for the rest of the summer to make a project of your own. What else would you like to know more about?
